        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1690",
        "content": "Tell him, there's seven hundred'll come marching into Marlborough Mills, the morning after he gives the five per cent, and will help him through his contract in no time.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
