        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1690",
        "content": "The medicines and treatment which dr Donaldson had ordered for mrs Hale, did her so much good at first that not only she herself, but Margaret, began to hope that he might have been mistaken, and that she could recover permanently.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1690_142293_000053_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1690/142293/1690_142293_000053_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1690",
        "content": "As for mr Hale, although he had never had an idea of the serious nature of their apprehensions, he triumphed over their fears with an evident relief, which proved how much his glimpse into the nature of them had affected him.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1690_142293_000053_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1690/142293/1690_142293_000053_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1690",
        "content": "Only Dixon croaked for ever into Margaret's ear.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1690_142293_000053_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1690/142293/1690_142293_000053_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1690",
        "content": "However, Margaret defied the raven, and would hope.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1690_142293_000054_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1690/142293/1690_142293_000054_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1690",
        "content": "They needed this gleam of brightness in doors, for out of doors, even to their uninstructed eyes, there was a gloomy brooding appearance of discontent.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1690_142293_000054_000001",
