        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1690",
        "content": "mr Hale had his own acquaintances among the working men, and was depressed with their earnestly told tales of suffering and long endurance.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1690_142293_000054_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1690/142293/1690_142293_000054_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1690",
        "content": "They would have scorned to speak of what they had to bear to any one who might, from his position, have understood it without their words.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1690_142293_000054_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1690/142293/1690_142293_000054_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1690",
        "content": "Margaret's whole soul rose up against him while he reasoned in this way-as if commerce were everything and humanity nothing.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1690_142293_000054_000008",
