        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1690",
        "content": "She could hardly, thank him for the individual kindness, which brought him that very evening to offer her-for the delicacy which made him understand that he must offer her privately-every convenience for illness that his own wealth or his mother's foresight had caused them to accumulate in their household, and which, as he learnt from dr Donaldson, mrs Hale might possibly require.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1690_142293_000054_000011",
