        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1690_142293_000054_000013",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1690/142293/1690_142293_000054_000013.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1690",
        "content": "She heard it in his grave and tremulous voice.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1690_142293_000054_000014",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1690/142293/1690_142293_000054_000014.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1690",
        "content": "How reconcile those eyes, that voice, with the hard reasoning, dry, merciless way in which he laid down axioms of trade, and serenely followed them out to their full consequences?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1690_142293_000054_000015",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1690/142293/1690_142293_000054_000015.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1690",
        "content": "The discord jarred upon her inexpressibly.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1690_142293_000054_000017",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1690/142293/1690_142293_000054_000017.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1690",
        "content": "To be sure, Nicholas Higgins, the father, spoke differently.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1690_142293_000054_000018",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1690/142293/1690_142293_000054_000018.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1690",
        "content": "He had been appointed a committee man, and said that he knew secrets of which the exoteric knew nothing.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1690_142293_000054_000023",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1690/142293/1690_142293_000054_000023.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1690",
        "content": "Her sister Mary was tying on her bonnet (in great clumsy bows, as suited her great clumsy fingers), to go to her fustian cutting, blubbering out loud the while, and evidently longing to be away from a scene that distressed her.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1690_142293_000054_000024",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1690/142293/1690_142293_000054_000024.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1690",
        "content": "Margaret came in upon this scene.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1690_142293_000054_000025",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1690/142293/1690_142293_000054_000025.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1690",
        "content": "She stood for a moment at the door-then, her finger on her lips, she stole to a seat on the squab near Bessy.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1690_142293_000054_000026",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1690/142293/1690_142293_000054_000026.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1690",
        "content": "Nicholas saw her come in, and greeted her with a gruff, but not unfriendly nod.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1690_142293_000054_000027",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1690/142293/1690_142293_000054_000027.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1690",
        "content": "Mary hurried out of the house catching gladly at the open door, and crying aloud when she got away from her father's presence.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1690_142293_000060_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1690/142293/1690_142293_000060_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1690",
        "content": "They had hardly uttered the sighing, that the eyes of each called to the other to bring up from the depths of her heart.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1690_142293_000060_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1690/142293/1690_142293_000060_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1690",
        "content": "At last Bessy said,",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1690_142293_000061_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1690/142293/1690_142293_000061_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1690",
        "content": "'I never thought to hear father call on God again.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1690_142293_000062_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1690/142293/1690_142293_000062_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1690",
        "content": "'Yes!' said Margaret. 'Let me bring you what money I can spare,--let me bring you a little food for that poor man's children.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1690_142293_000062_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1690/142293/1690_142293_000062_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1690",
        "content": "Don't let them know it comes from any one but your father.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1690_142293_000062_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1690/142293/1690_142293_000062_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1690",
        "content": "It will be but little.'",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1690_142293_000063_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1690/142293/1690_142293_000063_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1690",
        "content": "Bessy lay back without taking any notice of what Margaret said.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1690_142293_000063_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1690/142293/1690_142293_000063_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1690",
        "content": "She did not cry-she only quivered up her breath,",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1690_142293_000064_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1690/142293/1690_142293_000064_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1690",
        "content": "I can't make it out.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1690_142293_000065_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1690/142293/1690_142293_000065_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1690",
        "content": "Margaret sat utterly silent.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1690_142293_000065_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1690/142293/1690_142293_000065_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1690",
        "content": "How was she ever to go away into comfort and forget that man's voice, with the tone of unutterable agony, telling more by far than his words of what he had to suffer?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1690_142293_000065_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1690/142293/1690_142293_000065_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1690",
        "content": "She took out her purse; she had not much in it of what she could call her own, but what she had she put into Bessy's hand without speaking.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    }
]